<br>
I suspect we might be surprised at how many people, even here at the Grove, may fit this young man's basic profile.  Lack of real life social interaction, hours on EQ to substitute, low self esteem in RL, high self esteem inside Norrath, etc., etc.<br>
<br>
Things like this are a good wake up call.  It allows a good opportunity for everyone to step back and take a honest look in the mirrior and ask some tough questions of yourself.  Sort of like an alcoholic seeing a good friend die to alcohol related issues.<br>
<br>
All I can say is if the shoe fits, consider alternatives to EQ and possible help... if it doesnt and you play merely for fun the so be it.  It is all about how honest you choose to be with yourself.<br>
